Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: rawmidi: Make snd_rawmidi_transmit() race-free
Git-commit: 06ab30034ed9c200a570ab13c017bde248ddb2a6
Patch-mainline: 4.5-rc3
References: bsc#968018

